data.description: A lot of home for the money! 4 Br, 3Ba Block Home with over 2100sf of living area. Located on .35 acres, home is fenced, has a metal roof, large Kitchen with walk-in pantry, fireplace in the Master Bedroom, Laminate floors, and decorative ceiling fans. Plenty of room to play in the 23 x 53 detached workshop that has a full kitchen, entertainment bar and central heat/air. No hoa or deed restrictions.
